<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE CALL OF JESUS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu sapna aw chuh ngai un,
 Nanghaw migilo hungun;
 Chawlhna leh muonna hun pieng ka,
 &quot;Hungin, nanga ding ahi,&quot;
 A hukdamna chuh (3) nei dingin tuhin hungin. (2)

[V2]
 2. I chung thangvan sangtak akhun,
 Um mahleh A hun sam hi;
 Ginna'n A aw gi I he thei,
 &quot;Nangu migilo hungun&quot;
 A hukdamna chuh, (3) tuhin neiin kipak in. (2)

[V3]
 3. Sapna aw gi hai pai ta'n tin,
 Tuhin chuh A hun sam hi;
 Migilo sapna chuh ngaiin,
 Thisan hinna lam zuonin,
 A hukdamna chuh, (3) tuhin neiin kipak in. (2)

[V4]
 4. Isu kawm mai achun mu'n la,
 Hinna nanga ding tum chuh;
 Sesum leh dak-go khi lo a,
 Pathien thilthawn piek ahi,
 A hukdamna chuh, (3) tuhin neiin kipak in. (2)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>245</hymn_number>
</song>